542
00:36:43,560 --> 00:36:46,060
However, it's an unusual period now.

543
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:49,430
Taking a longer time to make the report is excusable.

544
00:36:49,430 --> 00:36:52,970
If there's an accident along the way and the report was never submitted to the capital,

545
00:36:52,970 --> 00:36:55,340
