558
00:38:27,670 --> 00:38:33,520
By the way, there's something I want to tell you.

559
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:37,230
I'm now the wife of Duke Cheng's heir apparent.

560
00:38:39,240 --> 00:38:42,390
